name: JayAmbe Engineering
overview:
Established in the year 1992, we,“Jay Ambe Engineering Works”, have created a niche in the industry by manufacturing and supplying a wide range of Plastic Packing Machinery and Sealing Machine. We offer a large number of products under this range that includes Bottom Sealing Machines and Side Sealing Machines.

Our Team: Technicians Engineers Quality Auditors Warehousing & Packaging Experts Skilled Labourers

Client Satisfaction: Sales is not only about gaining profit, it’s more about gaining customers’ satisfactions. Hence, we have always focused on manufacturing products that are in accordance with the customers’ requisite needs. For this, we conduct a stringent quality check of the entire range of products at different stages of production.

Our Quality: Over the years, we have gathered expertise and excellence in offering a quality-approved range of machines. These machines are offered with exceptional features in order to cater to the variegated needs of the customers.

Our Infrastructure: A well-equipped and technically sound infrastructure is the integral part of our organisation. We easily fulfil the bulk requirements of our customers by making use of advanced machinery and equipment. Our infrastructure is segregated into several units to maintain a swift rate of production.
